videos.description: Anthony J. Taylor finds his balance and gets into the end zone for a 12-yard touchdown reception to give the Bobcats the early lead in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Texas State's Taylor stumbles into end zone

videos.description: Devin Gentry catches the pass, breaks a tackle and stays on his feet for a 34-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Georgia State's Gentry breaks tackle for TD

videos.description: Damian Williams finds Chris French in the back of the end zone for  a 9-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Texas State's Williams throws second TD
